    <x-sections.card-image-with-text
        image="/images/digital-vinyl/custom-vinyl-shirts.jpg"
        alt="Full color digital vinyl shirts pressed in Joliet Illinois"
        title="Full Color Designs on Any Shirt"
    >
        <p class="mb-4">Digital vinyl printing lets us put full color, photo quality artwork directly onto shirts, hoodies, hats, and other garments, making it one of the most versatile methods in our <a href="/custom-apparel" class="link-notification">custom apparel</a> shop. The process starts with your design being printed in full color onto a special printable vinyl film, cut to shape and heat pressed onto the garment, much like our <a href="/custom-apparel/printing-options/dtf-printing" class="link-notification">DTF transfers</a> but with a slightly thicker hand feel and the ability to work on any fabric regardless of type. The result is a finish that holds every color, gradient, and fine detail in your original artwork.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">Standard cut vinyl works great for simple one or two color designs made up of solid shapes and text. Digital vinyl opens up a much wider range of creative possibilities because there are no limits on the number of colors and no need to separate artwork into individual layers. For businesses with detailed brand marks or artists creating custom apparel, digital vinyl is the clear choice, and our <a href="/design-services" class="link-notification">design team</a> can help build your artwork to get the most out of the process.</p>
        <p><a href="/" class="link-notification">Top 5 Percent</a> produces digital vinyl shirts for customers throughout Joliet, Shorewood, Crest Hill, Rockdale, and all of Will and DuPage County. Call us at <a href="tel:+18153498600" class="link-notification">(815) 349-8600</a> to talk about your design, or stop by 121 Springfield Avenue in Joliet.</p>
    </x-sections.card-image-with-text>

    <x-sections.card-image-with-text
        image="/images/digital-vinyl/custom-vinyl-hoodies.jpg"
        alt="Custom digital vinyl hoodies with full color artwork in Joliet and Shorewood Illinois"
        title="Digital Vinyl Hoodies and Sweatshirts"
        imagePosition="right"
    >
        <p class="mb-4">Digital vinyl hoodies give you the same photographic quality as digital vinyl shirts but on the heavier, more comfortable canvas of a pullover or zip-up hoodie, a popular option for <a href="/custom-apparel/group-wear/corporate-wear-shirts" class="link-notification">corporate wear</a> packages that include both shirts and outerwear. We press digital vinyl designs onto pullover hoodies, zip-up hoodies, crewneck sweatshirts, and fleece jackets for individuals, groups, and businesses throughout Joliet, Will and DuPage County. A hoodie with a detailed full color graphic makes a bold statement that stands apart from standard <a href="/custom-apparel/printing-options/embroidery" class="link-notification">embroidered</a> or screen printed apparel.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">Digital vinyl on hoodies works especially well for brand logos that include gradients or photographic elements that would be difficult or expensive to reproduce through other methods. Embroidery can only approximate complex color artwork, and digital vinyl handles all of it in a single print and press cycle, which keeps production time and cost reasonable. For group orders that include both hoodies and <a href="/custom-apparel/group-wear/spirit-wear-shirts" class="link-notification">spirit wear</a> jerseys, we can coordinate designs across all garment types for a unified look.</p>
        <p>We serve customers across Joliet, Shorewood, Plainfield, Romeoville, and the broader Chicagoland area. Whether you need one hoodie or a full set for your team, we are ready to help. Call <a href="tel:+18153498600" class="link-notification">(815) 349-8600</a> to get started on your digital vinyl hoodie order.</p>
    </x-sections.card-image-with-text>

    <x-sections.cta-quadruple-button-banner />

    <x-sections.card-2image-with-text
        image1="/images/digital-vinyl/vinyl-caps.jpg"
        alt1="Custom digital vinyl hats and caps in Joliet, Will and DuPage County Illinois"
