        alt2="Bold full color digital vinyl shirts in Joliet Illinois"
        title="Digital Vinyl on Hats, Caps, and More"
    >
        <p class="mb-4">Digital vinyl is not limited to flat garments, and our <a href="/custom-apparel" class="link-notification">custom apparel shop</a> in Joliet can press digital vinyl onto hats, caps, beanies, bags, and other accessories. A hat with a full color logo looks sharp and professional and is a popular item for <a href="/custom-apparel/group-wear/corporate-wear-shirts" class="link-notification">corporate wear</a> packages where businesses want to outfit their team with branded headwear. For events, digital vinyl hats let you put an intricate event design on headwear without the color restrictions that come with embroidery or other hat decoration methods.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">We also use digital vinyl for shirts and hoodies where bold neon colors, vivid artwork, or photographic content is part of the design. If you are creating merchandise for a band, an artist, or a <a href="/custom-apparel/group-wear/reunion-shirts" class="link-notification">reunion group</a> with complex artwork, digital vinyl gives you the production flexibility to do it right without requiring large minimum orders. You can order as few as one piece and get the same photographic quality on every item we press.</p>
        <p>Bring your design to us or let us help you develop something from scratch. We have an in-house design team ready to work with you on artwork that will look great pressed in digital vinyl on any garment you choose. Call <a href="tel:+18153498600" class="link-notification">(815) 349-8600</a> or visit 121 Springfield Avenue in Joliet.</p>
    </x-sections.card-2image-with-text>

    <x-sections.card-image-with-text
        image="/images/digital-vinyl/vinyl-zip-up-hoodies.jpg"
        alt="Custom digital vinyl zip-up hoodies and branded apparel in Joliet Illinois"
        title="Business Branding and Event Merchandise"
    >
        <p class="mb-4">Businesses throughout Joliet, Shorewood, and Will and DuPage County choose digital vinyl apparel when they want to put a full color logo on uniforms, giveaways, or branded merchandise, making it a popular companion to our <a href="/custom-apparel/group-wear/corporate-wear-shirts" class="link-notification">corporate wear</a> programs. Digital vinyl is one of the few decoration methods that can reproduce the full complexity of a brand identity system, including gradient fills and multi-tone color palettes, without compromise. Your brand looks exactly the way it should on every garment that leaves our shop, and our <a href="/design-services/logo-design" class="link-notification">logo design</a> team can help if you need your artwork built from scratch before production.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">Event organizers and merchandise sellers also rely on digital vinyl for items where the artwork is too complex for standard vinyl or where the event calls for a premium, detailed look. Concert shirts, tournament gear, memorial shirts, and fundraiser merchandise all benefit from the photographic quality digital vinyl provides. Check out our <a href="/promotional-items" class="link-notification">promotional items</a> to pair your digital vinyl apparel with branded mugs, tote bags, and giveaways for a complete event package.</p>
        <p>We are here to help businesses, teams, organizations, and individuals throughout Will and DuPage County and the Chicagoland area create apparel that represents them well. Call us at <a href="tel:+18153498600" class="link-notification">(815) 349-8600</a> or stop by 121 Springfield Avenue in Joliet to place your digital vinyl apparel order.</p>
    </x-sections.card-image-with-text>

